      </links>
      <content><![CDATA[<p>It's also possible to have different sites for each language. To share content between sites, it must be placed in the <code>/shared/</code> folder under the root site. With this option, it's possible to have similar approaches than described in Sections&nbsp;<a href="%(link0)">[independent_subsites]</a> and&nbsp;<a href="%(link1)">[sibling_subsites]</a>. Just set the <code>locale</code> property accordingly at the site's root folder.</p>]]></content>
